Colonization Screening Availability


Overview of Screening

Colonization testing for states in the the Antimicrobial Resistance (AR) Laboratory Networks Midwest Region is provided by the Wisconsin State Laboratory of Hygiene (WSLH), with support from CDC.

Scheduling of colonization screenings can be facilitated by your states Healthcare-Associated Infections (HAI) Program.
